| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4205 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: cbc2bb69-57a4-58e5-b14d-d5c4b5977e50"
